# ── Ghidra project / analysis artifacts ──────────────────────────────
*.rep/
*.gpr
*.lock
*.lock~
ghidra_*/                 # unpacked Ghidra installs (e.g. for the test harness)
.ghidra/
.ghidra.*

# ── Test harness scratch ─────────────────────────────────────────────
tests/generated/

# ── Java / build ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.class
bin/
build/
dist/
*.jar                     # keep none committed; the module ships source + .sla only

# ── IDE / editor ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
*.iml
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# ── OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# NOTE: 68HC16.sla IS intentionally committed (it is a generated artifact,
# compiled from 68HC16.slaspec) so the module works as a drop-in without a
# local SLEIGH compile. Ghidra auto-recompiles it if it is missing or stale.
